{
  "stem": "5313.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after this French jeep shows up, what happened after that?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened-- about two hours later, you know, trucks started to come with food and clothing and a lot of different thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people started to get to the sick people, you know, and started to put them into a truck and take them away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably took them in the hospital or whatever they could take care of them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in a matter of hours, you know, a lot of American cars and ambulances and all kind of help arrived at that time, which I might add, you know, at that time, which we find out is called the [INAUDIBLE] package.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, everybody was getting a little package which was marmalade, all kind of food in it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, you can imagine how we started to eat there, which I would say 99% of us was getting diarrhea, you know, a matter of hours, you know, after eating that food, you know, without bread.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it just was really a sickness that started to come out of us, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we find out, you know, that it's from the food, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put us at a hospital at that time, which I might add at that time, I was just, like I said, the strongest people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know-- probably was the doctor was giving me a big bottle of medicine to give everybody two pieces, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I started to do that, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't know what that was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I know that I have to give two piece to everybody that happened to be in that particular-- we called hospital.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a barrack.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
